      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via benchmark test cases at MRL 2 gradation.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed using the manufactured solution method for the Navier-Stokes equations in rotating reference frames. Observed convergence rates matched theoretical second-order accuracy. Benchmark results are documented in the solver verification report."
