      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for the hemolysis index QoI must be less than 5% at the operating points of interest.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted on the nominal impeller geometry at the five CPB operating points. GCI values for the relative hemolysis index ranged from 1.2% to 3.8%, all below the 5% threshold. The achieved level of 3 exceeds the required level of 2, providing additional confidence in spatial accuracy."
