      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must be documented and must correspond to the CPB operating envelope specified in the COU.",
      "rationale": "Bench validation experiments were conducted at flow rates of 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6 L/min and rotational speeds of 2000–3500 RPM, spanning the CPB operating envelope. Temperature, fluid viscosity, and hematocrit were controlled and recorded. Test conditions are fully documented in the validation test report."
    },
    {
