      "rationale": "Predicted RH values at all five operating points fell within the experimentally measured RH uncertainty bounds (±12%). The maximum absolute deviation between predicted and measured RH was 8.4%, within the acceptance band. Quantitative output comparison is documented in the validation summary report."
