      "rationale": "The primary QoI is the relative hemolysis index RH, which is the same metric specified in the COU acceptance criterion (RH < 1 relative to predicate device). Volume-averaged shear stress and exposure time are intermediate QoIs that feed directly into the hemolysis power-law model. QoI relevance is confirmed."
